Third-party brand assets
================================================================================

TerMinal bundles a small number of third-party brand logos so that the coding
agent / engine backing each session is identifiable at a glance in the UI
(see src/renderer/src/components/EngineLogo.tsx and src/renderer/src/assets/).

These marks are the property of their respective owners and are used here purely
for nominative identification of the tools TerMinal integrates with. Their
inclusion does not imply any affiliation with, sponsorship by, or endorsement by
those owners. TerMinal's own MIT license does NOT extend to these marks.

  - assets/claude.svg, assets/ai-tools/claude.png
      "Claude" and the Anthropic logo are trademarks of Anthropic PBC.
  - assets/openai.svg, assets/ai-tools/chatgpt.png
      The OpenAI / ChatGPT logos are trademarks of OpenAI, used to identify the
      Codex engine.
  - assets/cursor.png
      The Cursor logo is a trademark of Anysphere, Inc.
  - assets/hermes.svg
      Identifies the Hermes engine; property of its respective owner.

If you fork or redistribute TerMinal, review each owner's brand/trademark
guidelines. Remove or replace any mark you are not authorized to use.
